TITLE Hoist Static JSX Elements
HOIST STATIC JSX ELEMENTS
Extract static JSX outside components to avoid re-creation. 
Incorrect (recreates element every render): 
CODE tsx 192CHARS
Correct (reuses same element): 
CODE tsx 178CHARS
TI especially helpful for large and static SVG nodes, which can be expensive to recreate on every render. 
Note: IYPH React Compiler enabled, the compiler automatically hoists static JSX elements and optimizes component re-renders, making manual hoisting unnecessary. 